{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"塔里木之章——摘自“天山诗草”（冬不拉歌集）","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":12,"day":17}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔里木之章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——摘自“天山诗草”（冬不拉歌集）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔里木"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传说在很多年以前；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔里木是一座花园?，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠心的阿红牧主，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把枣儿汗吊在树上边；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她宁肯作一片落叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不和牧主结姻缘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣儿汗美丽像天仙?，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双星垂挂在耳边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长发仿佛是雏燕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑丝在水面倒垂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌喉像夜莺那样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱着“奴隶的心最美”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一位年青的奴隶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射出勇敢的一箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那箭像一粒火星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那箭把绳子射断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣儿汗轻轻落下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落在闪电似的马背。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣儿汗用小刀子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在树上刻下誓言——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“故乡呵等你变好了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我再投到你怀内”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的马如风急旋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长头发飘飞在双肩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿红在后面追赶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头发就变成河水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水咆哮起来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧主淹在浪涛里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪恶的宫殿倒了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成了万古的荒原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无缰之马奔跑千万年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才遇到英雄的骑手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"配上了金的鞍子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拴上了银的缰绳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴上了玉石笼头?，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把枣儿汗接回到新乐园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?塔里木，维吾尔语，意思是无缰之马。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?枣儿汗，姑娘的名字，意思是星星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?新疆农垦兵团在一九五六年夏天、一九"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五七年冬天，分别由尉犁（维语孔雀）、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿克苏（维语白水）向塔里木腹地进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军，开发原始森林，并向沙海搏斗，修"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑无数水渠、水库，在塔里木河上架起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大桥，开垦了几百万亩荒地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"* 咆［páo］"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野杏树开花的时节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军曾到过瀚海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他用锐敏的目光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在探索戈壁的未来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把土捧到手上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尝了一尝：“有点咸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这地还是不坏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土质胜过南泥湾。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军豪迈的脚步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏出了一条红线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他和他的战友们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向风沙世界来挑战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人说：“这里能种树。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军说：“不但要种树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要造个人工湖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再把大头鱼养起来。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁像一道铁门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要用勇敢的钥匙开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孔雀站在铁门关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双翅扑向棉田麦海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军将柳枝攀折，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光在手上摇曳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孔雀呵，展翅吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军登上了山顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他送来一串绿宝石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送给你来作飘带。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雁讯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古木参天的河沿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芦苇上飞来大雁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雁掠过了水面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旋即又跃上蓝天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“青年人你有什么话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我捎回到中原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是鹿角还是长绒棉？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是歌声还是河水？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"答——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我手上有一把土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒原上的一把黑土。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它染着我的热汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它暖着我的心肝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个幸福人的影子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"印在它的上面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个垦荒者的志愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写在它的中间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土呵塔里木的土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它比奶汁还要鲜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土呵塔里木的土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是天鹅撒下的花瓣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的将军尝过它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再请故乡人看一看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是这一把土呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请把它寄到河南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是有人问我住在哪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我住在这红楼上面！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}